name: Subterranean Assault
description: Stir a group of shalk that attack after 3 seconds, dealing 3240 Poison Damage to enemies in front of you.  After the shalk complete their attack, they burrow underground for 3 seconds and then resurface again, dealing 3240 Poison Damage to enemies in front of you.
effectLines: Converts to a Stamina ability and deals Poison Damage. The shalk burrow after attacking, and attack again after a delay.
